description: Modelon AB (publ) is a SE-based company operating in Software industry. The company is headquartered in Lund, Skane. The company went IPO on 2021-04-28. Modelon AB, located in Lund, Sweden, provides information technology services. The company offers model-based systems engineering solutions for the automotive, industrial equipment, aerospace and defence, energy and process, academia and research industries. The company offers Modelica and FMI open standards, which enables customers leverage their tools of choice.
name: Modelon AB (publ)
